She was the daughter of saint Vincent of junior clubs the netherlands and santa Valdetrude and was the nephew of st. Aldegonda.He married Valdeberto VI of Lommois Major Saints Ancestry (his maternal uncle) and it would be the mother of Valdberto VII of Lommois. A widow entered the Abbey of Mauberge, of which she became abbess in 684, going on to the aunt Aldegonda, a position which he retained until his death. She was succeeded by sister Madelberta or Amalberga.
